      "end": 148.23,
      "text": "하셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.23,
      "end": 149.89,
      "text": "어떠세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.19,
      "end": 152.63,
      "text": "I didn't realize how fun it is to speak English"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.63,
      "end": 154.75,
      "text": "until I started doing GMP"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.75,
      "end": 157.83,
      "text": "and the more I do it the better I get at English"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.83,
      "end": 160.29,
      "text": "and also I can use English more at home"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.29,
      "end": 163.85,
      "text": "그러니까 우리도 이렇게 keep practicing 할 수가 있는 거잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.85,
      "end": 164.23,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.23,
      "end": 166.79,
      "text": "와 참 좋네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.79,
      "end": 167.69,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.69,
      "end": 169.17,
      "text": "I like it"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.17,
      "end": 171.27,
      "text": "I like using my native language"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.27,
      "end": 172.89,
      "text": "역시 원어민이었구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.89,
      "end": 173.97,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.97,
      "end": 176.47,
      "text": "정체성을 깨달으시는 순간이군요"
