    {
      "start": 364.54,
      "end": 365.2,
      "text": "Again?"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.46,
      "end": 367.38,
      "text": "Wait, she already had three strikes"
    },
    {
      "start": 367.38,
      "end": 368.68,
      "text": "Three strikes and you're out"
    },
    {
      "start": 368.68,
      "end": 369.78,
      "text": "어, 그러면 지금"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.78,
      "end": 371.06,
      "text": "네 번째 늦은 거니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.06,
      "end": 371.96,
      "text": "이제 큰일 났어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.96,
      "end": 373.64,
      "text": "Your fourth time being late"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.64,
      "end": 374.78,
      "text": "어, 근데 이번에도"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.78,
      "end": 376.88,
      "text": "she had to do with her family"
    },
    {
      "start": 376.88,
      "end": 378.0,
      "text": "And this time she had"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.0,
      "end": 378.98,
      "text": "a special situation"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.98,
      "end": 379.42,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.42,
      "end": 380.58,
      "text": "Her parents were being"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.58,
      "end": 382.28,
      "text": "interviewed by a TV station"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.28,
      "end": 384.7,
      "text": "And of course they can't talk"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.7,
      "end": 385.9,
      "text": "So they needed her"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.9,
      "end": 386.7,
      "text": "to interpret"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.7,
      "end": 388.02,
      "text": "their sign language"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.02,
      "end": 388.38,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.38,
      "end": 389.78,
      "text": "Which is why she was late"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.78,
      "end": 391.0,
      "text": "But her teacher"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.0,
      "end": 391.88,
      "text": "doesn't know about that"
    },
    {
      "start": 391.88,
      "end": 393.38,
      "text": "I was really worried"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.38,
      "end": 394.22,
      "text": "about her this time"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.22,
      "end": 395.42,
      "text": "음, 그래서 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.42,
      "end": 396.92,
      "text": "루비가 레슨 시간에"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.92,
      "end": 397.48,
      "text": "늦다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.48,
      "end": 398.82,
      "text": "막 뛰어가가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.82,
      "end": 400.34,
      "text": "메르나르도 선생님의"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.34,
      "end": 401.92,
      "text": "집을 두들깁니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.92,
      "end": 403.42,
      "text": "I was afraid"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.42,
      "end": 405.02,
      "text": "Yeah, he wouldn't open the door"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.02,
      "end": 406.6,
      "text": "Yeah, I was really"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.6,
      "end": 407.54,
      "text": "I felt for her"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.54,
      "end": 409.32,
      "text": "I really felt for her this time"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.32,
      "end": 409.92,
      "text": "저도요"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.92,
      "end": 411.02,
      "text": "Because she was honestly"
    },
    {
      "start": 411.02,
